data.description: Fall in love with this charming 4 bedroom, 2 bath home on a spacious lot! Open dining room with large picture window lets in lots of natural light, and is conveniently located right off of the eat-in kitchen.  Kitchen has stainless appliances with new oven recently installed, and has custom built-ins making for the perfect coffee bar area.  Sunken living room is the absolute coziest spot in the home and great for all your large gatherings with a woodburning fireplace.  Master bedroom is spacious with spa-like master bath attached and a walk-in closet.  You will love the finished loft space that is perfect for a kids play room or a game room!   Enjoy a lazy day on the porch bed swing on the covered patio, with easy access to the large backyard with above ground pool and bonus shop!
